        "timestamp": "2018-07-20 07:56:51.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n@Libo, it goes in reception.reception-handling.reception-handling-sdc. Please work in that module. Would you be able to submit a draft of the module layout you propose in there or else maybe out a small sketch up in the wiki?",
