        "timestamp": "2018-07-20 11:22:59.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n> @Libo, it goes in reception.reception-handling.reception-handling-sdc.\n > Please work in that module. Would you be able to submit a draft of\n > the module layout you propose in there or else maybe out a small\n > sketch up in the wiki?\n\nhi, Liam, \ni'll put them into https://github.com/vmmqa/XenGT-CitrixServer-patch/tree/master/study/hello-world the github. you could have a check.\n\nwhy there is reception-handling-sdc under reception-handling? does policy plan to register as another client? \n\nbtw,  for aai side, they are  under aai/model-loader/ dir ;\nfor so side, they are under so/asdc-controller dir.",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
      {
        "id": "fdf583aa5a3dc1364375bf03de9099b512f95818",
